snippet.textDisplay:
When I first listened to this sad song I cried a lot. The melody of the song made me feel like I am part of Italy, made me feel like I am an Italian, sharing the pain of the Italian people.
Even thought I do not understand the lyrics but I can use Google to translate into English to understand. I would like to try to someday sing it in Vietnamese because I am Vietnamese American.
I share the same religion as most Italian. I am a Catholic. May God bless Italy,may God bless our Pope!
